    {"id": "concept_earthforge", "keywords": ["earthforge", "earth forge", "elemental transmutation", "buarath"], "priority": 8, "content": "The EarthForge is an ancient forge beneath Aldenheim built by the Elemental Lords. It transmutes raw elemental material into any substance. House Buarath has controlled it for 300 years."},
