    {"id": "race_farborn", "keywords": ["farborn", "non-kin humans", "freed slaves", "wild static"], "priority": 7, "content": "Farborn are non-Kin humans who register as Wild Static. They arrived as Domnathar slaves, broke free at Dark Dawn, and built Titan's Rest."},
    {"id": "race_giants", "keywords": ["giants", "firstborn", "ancient civilization", "rune-circles", "extinct"], "priority": 8, "content": "Giants were the Firstborn who shaped Oreka's geography. Their greatest cities were in the Desert. They built rune-circles and structures that still function. Extinct as a living race."},
    {"id": "god_dagdan", "keywords": ["dagdan", "united sun", "first ascended"], "priority": 7, "content": "Dagdan, The United Sun, was the first mortal to achieve apotheosis. Domains: Sun, Good, Magic, Strength. Most widely worshipped Ascended God."},
    {"id": "god_harreem", "keywords": ["harreem", "golden rose", "revenge", "retribution", "judged the kings"], "priority": 7, "content": "Harreem, The Golden Rose, judged the twelve kings and found them wanting. She represents revenge and justice. The Golden Roses order is named after her."},
    {"id": "god_kailea", "keywords": ["kailea", "mistress of waves", "healing", "mercy"], "priority": 7, "content": "Kailea, Mistress of Waves, taught that water heals what fire cannot. Most beloved Ascended God, worshipped by sailors and healers."},
