    {"id": "city_highridge", "keywords": ["highridge", "scorchspires", "taraf-imro stronghold"], "priority": 7, "content": "Highridge (6,000) is the Taraf-Imro stronghold. Produces Embersteel Blades. A Deceiver artifact burns in the lava tubes beneath it."},
